<div id="header">
<h1>MLtonWord</h1>
</div>
<div id="content">
<div class="listingblock">
<div class="content">
<pre class="rouge highlight"><code data-lang="sml"><span class="kr">signature</span> <span class="nn">MLTON_WORD</span> <span class="p">=</span>
   <span class="kr">sig</span>
      <span class="kr">type</span> <span class="kt">t</span>

      <span class="kr">val</span> <span class="nv">bswap</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">t</span> <span class="p">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">t</span>
      <span class="kr">val</span> <span class="nv">rol</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">t</span> <span class="n">*</span> <span class="n">word</span> <span class="p">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">t</span>
      <span class="kr">val</span> <span class="nv">ror</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">t</span> <span class="n">*</span> <span class="n">word</span> <span class="p">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">t</span>
   <span class="kr">end</span></code></pre>
</div>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>type t</code></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>the type of words.  For <code>MLton.LargeWord</code> this is <code>LargeWord.word</code>,
for <code>MLton.Word</code> this is <code>Word.word</code>, for <code>MLton.Word8</code> this is
<code>Word8.word</code>, for <code>MLton.Word16</code> this is <code>Word16.word</code>, for
<code>MLton.Word32</code> this is <code>Word32.word</code>, for <code>MLton.Word64</code> this is
<code>Word64.word</code>.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li>
<p><code>bswap w</code></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>byte swap.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li>
<p><code>rol (w, w')</code></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>rotates left (circular).</p>
</div>
</li>
<li>
<p><code>ror (w, w')</code></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>rotates right (circular).</p>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
